# ZATCA Go Integration
#
# All ZATCA configuration (credentials, CSR, seller info) is stored
# in the database. Only a database connection string (DSN) is needed.
#
# Pass the DSN via CLI flag:
#   --dsn "user:pass@tcp(host:port)/dbname"
#
# Or via environment variables:
#   DSN=user:pass@tcp(host:port)/dbname
#
# Or individually:
#   HOST=localhost
#   PORT=3306
#   DBUSER=root
#   PASSWORD=secret
#   DBNAME=mydb
